<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="greeting-n">greeting <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡriːtɪŋ/    美 /'ɡriːtɪŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>问候；致意；迎接：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>exchanged greetings</strong> (= greeted each other) and sat down to lunch.
他们互相问候，然后坐下来共进午餐</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She waved a friendly greeting.
她友好地挥手致意。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She raised her hand <strong>in greeting</strong>.
她举起手来打招呼。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[复数] 祝词；贺词；问候语：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Christmas / birthday greetings</strong>
圣诞/生日贺词</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My mother sends her greetings to you all.
我母亲向你们大家问好。</p></div></div>